68w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Balance is a modern WordPress WooCommerce theme suitable for your online business. It has premium-like eCommerce features, homepage layout options, custom landing page templates, and more.</p>\n<p>It offers multiple page layouts for your shop and products. It comes with 6 color skins, social widgets, Google Fonts support, and a custom logo area. Balance is fully optimized for speed and performance.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/woocommerce-hotel/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Hotel\" rel=\"nofollow\">22. Hotel</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/woocommerce-hotel/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Hotel\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/hotel.jpg\" alt=\"Hotel\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222206\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/hotel.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/hotel-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/hotel-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Hotel is another child theme of Storefront WooCommerce theme. It&#8217;s suitable to create WooCommerce shops for hotels, hostels, guest houses, and other hospitality services. It display a featured image on the homepage including welcome message and a call-to-action button just below the navigation menu.</p>\n<p>You can use the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/woomarketing-bundle/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WooMarketing bundle\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooMarketing bundle</a> to boost marketing for your online store. It comes with email marketing services, smart discount options, checkout with social profiles, and more.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojomarketplace-wpoutlaw/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Outlaw\" rel=\"nofollow\">23. Outlaw</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojomarketplace-wp